parameters: Would you like to skip the epilogue of Episode 2?
\F[beni_smile]\FF[wata_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "It was tough... carrying you all the way here."

\F[yuri_smile]\FF[wata_trouble]\AA[1]Yurika: "Good thing I remembered there was a stretcher in
the infirmary."

\F[beni_smile]\FF[wata_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "Yeah. But if you had remained a monster... you might
have involved everyone else. That's not what you would have
wanted, right, Cotton?"

\F[beni_smile]\FF[wata_trouble]\AA[2]Wata: "I wanted everyone... to enjoy being close together in
tight spaces... just like me."

\F[nako_trouble]\FF[wata_trouble]\AA[2]Wata: "Right...? Because... it feels good... it's calming...
being inside a locker..."
\F[nako_trouble]\FF[wata_trouble]\AA[2]Wata: "But maybe that's just me... I thought..."

\F[nako_trouble]\FF[wata_trouble]\AA[2]Wata: "But then... I made friends... and I was happy. Even
if I'm not human... that's okay with me..."

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[wata_trouble]\AA[2]Wata: "No... because the only things that hide in lockers
are... spirits, as Senpai Nitori said..."

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[wata_trouble]\AA[2]Wata: "I'm the same as a spirit... so the monster was...
me..."

\F[yuri_trouble]\FF[wata_trouble]\AA[1]Yurika: "...Her mental care seems to be a deep-rooted
issue."
\F[nako_trouble]\FF[wata_trouble]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Is she going to turn into a monster again?"

\F[yuri_trouble]\FF[wata_trouble]\AA[1]Yurika: "I'm sorry. But I believe there will come a time
when you can be true to yourself without any pretense. Your
feelings are very... pure."

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[wata_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: (The fact that the president can only offer
comfort...)

\F[yuri_smile]\FF[wata_trouble]\AA[1]Yurika: "If you ever have any troubles, feel free to come to
the student council room. We'll always be waiting."

\F[yuri_smile]Yurika: "Now, if you'll excuse me. I'll leave the rest to
you... Suzaku-san, Byakko-san."

\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "She ran away...? Well, there's nothing more we can
do..."

\F[nako_smile]Nadeshiko: "Yeah... Cotton, I can only say the same thing as
the student council president, but if you're troubled, rely
on us."
\F[nako_smile]Nadeshiko: "We'll always be there to support you... Really."
???: "Unfortunately, you cannot be of help to her."
\F[beni_angry]\FF[king_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "What are you planning to do with Cotton!!"
\F[beni_angry]\FF[king_smile]\AA[1]Akane: (I can't transform in front of Nadeshiko!!)

\F[beni_angry]\FF[king_smile]\AA[2]???: "A wish made with a pure heart... must come true. You
think so too, don't you?"
\F[beni_angry]\FF[king_smile]\AA[2]???: "Her wish can only be fulfilled in the 'Kingdom'."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[king_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "'Kingdom'...!! You're the monster plotting to take
over this school, aren't you!!"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[king_smile]\AA[2]???: "You wouldn't understand. You who harbor a wicked
secret."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[king_smile]\AA[2]???: "You are the one who is most blind to yourself, Akane
Suzaku. That's why you cannot reach me."

\FF[king_smile]???: "Come, let's go together. To the paradise you desire...
where no one will deny you."

\F[wata_smile]\FF[king_smile]\AA[2]???: "Yes! Everything will be as you wish. This gold coin is
for you."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[nako_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "She was taken away... damn it! Right before my
eyes!!"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[nako_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "Don't worry, Nadeshiko... I'll definitely save
her!!"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[nako_trouble]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Against such a monster... what can you do,
Akane...?"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[nako_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "I want you to believe me. I will never give up on
Cotton."
